Cell["\<\
Once you have logged in,  you can connect under a different username using \
the CONNECT command.The username and password must be valid for the database. \
For example, to connect the username TODD to the default database using the \
password FOX, you could enter:
\t-CONNECT TODD
\t-You are prompted to enter the password, FOX.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.779293963836656*^9, 3.779294010484007*^9}, {
   3.779294043406046*^9, 3.7792940525672297`*^9}, 
   3.779629142910428*^9},ExpressionUUID->"044ced4b-18c7-4134-a984-\
f8be2cfa0e74"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Use the SHOW statement to find out what databases currently exist on the \
server :\
\>", "Item",
