Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["\n",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 "to discover where the Java drivers should be placed, run in the Mathematica \
notebook\n\n$InstallationDirectory\n\nThe standard installation directory \
should be :\n\nC:\[Backslash]Program Files\[Backslash]Wolfram Research\
\[Backslash]Mathematica\[Backslash]14.3\n\nThen, you should search for a \
folder structure of something like:\[NonBreakingSpace]\n\n\
\[NonBreakingSpace]SystemFiles > Links > DatabaseLink > Java"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8553042266196423`*^9, 3.855304277651926*^9}, {
  3.855386681390052*^9, 3.8553866912048597`*^9}, {3.8553867273811493`*^9, 
